[normal]Th
[normal]e development of CCS clusters/networks – enabling industrial sectors to link in to pre-existing transport and 
[normal]storage infrastructure - will ensure cost-effective decarbonisation of industrial sectors. This is particularly important as many of these sectors cannot afford the full cost of fitting CCS.
